Step 1: 
    go to Infrastructure → Hosts

Step 2: 
      Chose your OS and Deploy OneAgent

Step 3:
      Now Click on update button 

Step 4:
      Now you can click install button and it will show One Agent install steps

Step 5:
     Again chose your OS type

Step 6:
     Chose Archeture type of your application OR infrastructure

Step 7:
     Chose monitoring mode Fullstack, Insfrastructure and Discovery

Step 8:
      Now click the Generate token button it will create token to install One Agent

Step 9:
     Copy the link and paste where you need to install the one agent it will download the one agent

Step 10:
      Verify signature the of one agent

Step 11:
      Install OneAgent as the privileged user
